</head>
<body>
    <div class="portal-container">
        <div class="portal-card legal-card">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/>
                    <path d="M19 12H5"/>
                </svg>
                Back to Login
            </a>
            
            <div class="portal-header" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">
                <h1 style="font-size: 1.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">How we handle your data</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="legal-content">
                <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>When you use our guest WiFi network, we collect the following information:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Email address or phone number used for authentication</li>
                    <li><strong>Personal Details:</strong> Name (if provided)</li>
                    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> MAC address, device type, operating system, browser information</li>
                    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Connection times, data usage, session duration</li>
                    <li><strong>Network Data:</strong> IP addresses assigned, websites visited (for security monitoring)</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Provide, maintain, and improve the WiFi service</li>
                    <li>Authenticate users and prevent unauthorized access</li>
                    <li>Monitor network security, detect threats, and prevent abuse</li>
                    <li>Analyze network performance and troubleshoot issues</li>
                    <li>Comply with legal and regulatory requirements</li>
                    <li>Communicate important service updates if necessary</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Data Retention</h2>
                <p>We retain different types of data for different periods:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Connection logs:</strong> 90 days (for security and troubleshooting)</li>
                    <li><strong>Personal information:</strong> 12 months (unless deletion requested)</li>
                    <li><strong>Aggregated analytics:</strong> Indefinitely (anonymized data)</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
                <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. We may share data with:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Third parties who assist in operating our network infrastructure</li>
                    <li><strong>Legal authorities:</strong> When required by law, court order, or legal process</li>
                    <li><strong>Property management:</strong> For security purposes and incident investigation</li>
                    <li><strong>Emergency services:</strong> In case of safety concerns</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Your Rights</h2>
                <p>Under applicable data protection laws, you have the right to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
                    <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
                    <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
                    <li><strong>Restriction:</strong> Request limitation of processing</li>
                    <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a structured format</li>
                    <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to processing of your data</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Security Measures</h2>
                <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Encryption of data in transit and at rest</li>
                    <li>Regular security assessments and updates</li>
                    <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
                    <li>Staff training on data protection</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
                <p>Our captive portal uses essential cookies to maintain your session. We do not use tracking cookies or third-party analytics on the portal itself.</p>

                <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
                <p>Our service is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

                <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by posting the new policy on this page.</p>

                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <p>For privacy-related inquiries, data access requests, or to exercise your rights, please contact <strong><%= companyName %></strong>.</p>

                <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 2026</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Background decoration -->
        <div class="bg-decoration" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="circle circle-1"></div>
            <div class="circle circle-2"></div>
            <div class="circle circle-3"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
